OL,3,CInternational crime gang's #3 million
OL,4,C'chop shop' shut down by police
OL,6,FAn international organised crime gang
OL,7,Fwho stole #3 million worth of luxury
OL,8,Fcars while also receiving Government
OL,9,Floans during the pandemic has been
OL,10,Fshut down by police.
OL,12,FRange Rovers, Mercedes, and BMWs were
OL,13,Fall stolen from driveways and shopping
OL,14,Fcentres and broken down to parts in a
OL,15,Fhidden garage in Oldham, Greater
OL,16,FManchester.
