OL,3,CInternational crime gang's #3 million
OL,4,C'chop shop' shut down by police
OL,6,FThe ringleader of the conspiracy and
OL,7,Ffive other men were jailed in January
OL,8,F2022. Then, a judge expressed his
OL,9,Fdisbelief after it was revealed that
OL,10,Fthe OCG's leader, Asif Hussain, had
OL,11,Fbeen able to secure a #50,000 Covid
OL,12,Floan offered by the Government to help
OL,13,Fbusinesses struggling during the
OL,14,Fpandemic.
OL,16,FNow, a further seven members of the
OL,17,Fgang have been sentenced for their
OL,18,Fpart in the scheme.
