OL,3,CInternational crime gang's #3 million
OL,4,C'chop shop' shut down by police
OL,6,FThe judge described the outfit as
OL,7,F"highly professional" and "well
OL,8,Forganised", using "sophisticated
OL,9,Fequipment" to commit their crimes.
OL,11,FThe 'chop shops', where stolen cars
OL,12,Fwere broken down, were discovered by
OL,13,Fpolice in old mills in Oldham and
OL,14,FBury, as well as a unit in Wigan. The
OL,15,Fcars were often stolen in horrendous
OL,16,Fcircumstances.
