OL,6,FOne man at home in Failsworth with his
OL,7,Fthree-year-old daughter was told he
OL,8,Fwould be killed if he went outside to
OL,9,Finvestigate as thieves stole his
OL,10,FMercedes, the 2022 hearing was told.
OL,12,FAmong those sentenced in court on
OL,13,FFriday was Asif Matadar, who was part
OL,14,Fof the "professional team of car
OL,15,Fthieves".
