OL,6,FThe judge said he had displayed a
OL,7,F"breathtaking piece of criminal
OL,8,Farrogance' when in May 2020, just
OL,9,Fhours after attending a police
OL,10,Fcompound to collect a car in his name,
OL,11,Fhe was involved in the theft of a
OL,12,FVolvo in broad daylight.
OL,14,FShewaz Rehman was in a WhatsApp group
OL,15,Fnamed 'The Company', in which the gang
OL,16,Fdiscussed their criminal plots. When
OL,17,Fhe was 'chopping' one particular Range
OL,18,FRover, Adam Elwood filmed a video clip
OL,19,Fwhere he 'boasted' that it was 'the
OL,20,Fbeginning of the end' for the car.
