OL,6,FAfter the hearing, Detective Constable
OL,7,FAllan Barker, from Greater Manchester
OL,8,FPolice's Serious Organised Crime
OL,9,FGroup, said: "This has been a long and
OL,10,Fcomplex investigation, and I am
OL,11,Fgrateful to the Crown Prosecution
OL,12,FService who have given their time,
OL,13,Fexpertise, and insight throughout this
OL,14,Fentire process. I am particularly
OL,15,Fgrateful to our victims who came
OL,16,Fforward and enabled us to bring such a
OL,17,Fstrong case against these men.
