OL,6,F"This gang were extremely organised
OL,7,Fand had sophisticated connections in
OL,8,Fprominent areas across the globe,
OL,9,Fmeaning they were able to ship
OL,10,Fmillions of pounds of stolen cars and
OL,11,Fvehicle parts overseas. The
OL,12,Ftransnational nature of this group
OL,13,Fmeant international collaboration was
OL,14,Fessential to this investigation, and
OL,15,Fultimately led to the arrest these men.
OL,17,F"We will continue to collaborate and
OL,18,Fshare intelligence with our
OL,19,Finternational partners to make sure no
OL,20,Fone gets off lightly and they face
OL,21,Fjustice for their crimes at home."
